  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Product Development Baker",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role</strong><br />We are seeking a versatile individual with both science and practical baking skills to join our test bakery team.<br /></p><p><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Plan, conduct and analyse bake trials using scientific methods and analytical equipment</li><li>Prepare and bake bread, cake and pastry samples for testing and customer demonstrations</li><li>Develop, test and scale new recipes and prototypes including functional ingredients such as emulsifiers, raising agents</li><li>Perform sensory evaluations, taste panels and technical comparisons to optimise product quality</li><li>Generate technical reports and presentations to communicate findings internally and externally</li><li>Support sales and customer teams with troubleshooting and bakery-related enquiries </li><li>Decorate and finalise baked products for presentation</li><li>Ensure high standards of hygiene, sanitation and workplace safety</li><li>Contribute to recipe modifications and continuous improvement to meet evolving customer needs</li><li>perform ad hoc duties as required</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Diploma in Food Science, Food Technology, Baking or related field</li><li>Min 3 years experience in bakery production, product development or food technology</li><li>Strong knowledge of baking techniques, product analysis and industry trends</li><li>Creative, motivated customer-focused and able to work independently</li><li>Excellent communication, interpersonal and teamwork skills</li><li>Passion for baking and innovation with attention to detail</li></ul>",
